Usage: tnt [ FORCE | OFF ] [ SERIAL ]

TNT trap-handler replaces software error requesters with debug requester
FORCE replaces even unknown (non-dos/exec) trap handlers
SERIAL adds serial output of any software error before displaying requester

Version 37.2 adds SegTracker support ! (Segtracker comes with Enforcer)

Warning: turn TNT off before using a trap-based debugger

